---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="Scribble">
  <Container>
    <div class="text-center mt-20 mb-20">
      <div class="w-10 h-1 bg-rose-300 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full"></div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-800 mb-6">
        Scribble
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-stone-500 font-light">
        자유롭게 끄적이는 개인적인 메모장입니다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-yellow-50/50 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-yellow-100/50 relative">
        <div class="text-xs text-yellow-600/50 font-bold mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Today's Note</div>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
          "하고 싶은 일을 하려면 하기 싫은 일을 해야해. 그런데 하기 싫은 일을 하기 위해선 하고 싶어야 해"
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-stone-100">
        <div class="text-xs text-stone-400 font-bold mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Today's Note</div>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
          "We can be heroes, just for one day"
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>